# Local dev: leave unset — the app calls `/api` and Vite proxies to your backend (see vite.config.ts).
# Vite dev proxy target (default http://127.0.0.1:8080):
# VITE_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8080

# Production build: public backend origin ONLY (no path). Fetches go to `${VITE_API_BASE_URL}/api/...`.
# Example: VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://dodge-o2c-api.onrender.com
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
